name: Apple iPhone 13 Pro Max
description: The Apple iPhone 13 Pro Max features a 6.7-inch Super Retina XDR display, A15 Bionic chip, Pro camera system with 12MP Ultra Wide, Wide, and Telephoto cameras, Night mode, Deep Fusion, ProRAW, 4K Dolby Vision HDR recording, and more.

name: Samsung Galaxy Watch 4
description: The Samsung Galaxy Watch 4 features a 1.4-inch Super AMOLED display, Exynos W920 dual-core processor, 16GB storage, 5ATM + IP68 water resistance, heart rate and sleep tracking, and more.

name: Bose QuietComfort 35 II Wireless Headphones
description: The Bose QuietComfort 35 II Wireless Headphones feature world-class noise cancellation, Bluetooth and NFC pairing with voice prompts, up to 20 hours of battery life, and Alexa and Google Assistant compatibility.

name: Apple AirPods Pro
description: Experience the magic of AirPods with noise-cancelling technology and a customizable fit. With transparency mode, you can hear what's happening around you while still enjoying your music or phone call. The AirPods Pro are easy to set up with all your Apple devices, and the charging case provides up to 24 hours of battery life.

name: Amazon Echo Dot (4th Gen)
description: The 4th generation Amazon Echo Dot is a smart speaker with Alexa that fits perfectly into any room. You can ask Alexa to play music, answer questions, control smart home devices, and more. With a new spherical design and improved sound quality, the Echo Dot is the perfect addition to your home.
